00:40:28.868 --> 00:40:31.548
sort of glory days, and they're still happening.

724
00:40:31.568 --> 00:40:32.948
The glory days are now.

725
00:40:34.028 --> 00:40:37.668
We're going to be talking about analyses of thousands of cancer whole genomes, and

726
00:40:37.728 --> 00:40:38.008
I think

727
00:40:38.908 --> 00:40:42.228
while we are excited about that, I think we also have to think about

728
00:40:43.408 --> 00:40:46.978
why aren't we analyzing hundreds of thousands or millions of cancer whole genomes?

729
00:40:47.028 --> 00:40:50.748
And I think a lot of the questions that we're asking, the really deep,

