01:12:57.904 --> 01:13:01.624
and others had less, but we filtered all of these mutations

1281
01:13:01.744 --> 01:13:01.974
out

1282
01:13:03.264 --> 01:13:07.144
from the data. So we want first to make sure

1283
01:13:07.204 --> 01:13:09.144
that we're seeing something that makes sense, kind of.

1284
01:13:09.224 --> 01:13:12.844
So we look at all the-- this is 85 or

1285
01:13:12.924 --> 01:13:16.804
8,500 tumors, roughly, or more than 8,000 different tumor

1286
01:13:16.824 --> 01:13:20.584
types. And you see the different substitutions, and as we expect,

