01:13:32.704 --> 01:13:35.724
cancer and the C to A substitutions in

1291
01:13:36.844 --> 01:13:36.944
the

1292
01:13:37.964 --> 01:13:41.608
lung cancers.Then we looked at the double nucleotide variations.

