1377
01:18:40.328 --> 01:18:44.248
And then there are the ugly QQ plots, which are either inflated P value

1378
01:18:44.288 --> 01:18:48.108
or deflated, caused by essentially bad

1379
01:18:48.188 --> 01:18:51.248
statistical models that you need to kind of fix.

1380
01:18:51.998 --> 01:18:54.808
And so here's the example of colorectal cancer.

