1462
01:23:46.356 --> 01:23:49.856
So TMPRSS2 and SLC45A3 and

1463
01:23:49.876 --> 01:23:53.416
FOXA1 are highly expressed in normal prostate.

1464
01:23:53.436 --> 01:23:57.376
Here, this is GTEx data. But also SLC30A4 is

