01:23:57.436 --> 01:24:01.316
highly expressed, suggesting that this is another mechanism to take a

1466
01:24:01.355 --> 01:24:05.286
kind of a regulatory region of highly expressed gene and move it

1467
01:24:05.316 --> 01:24:08.996
next to ETV1 to overexpress ETV1 in prostate cancer.

1468
01:24:09.616 --> 01:24:13.256
